{title:Version}

{pstd}
{cmd:reg2tex} version 1.0.3 - 10 September 2025{p_end}
{pstd}{ul:Updates}:{p_end}
{phang2}- Added comparison section with regtex{p_end}
{phang2}- Added acknowledgment section{p_end}
{phang2}- Fixed starlevels conversion to handle any number of levels (1-3){p_end}
{phang2}- Added special handling for addnotes option to ensure proper quoting{p_end}
{phang2}- Converted threeline option to booktabs option for esttab{p_end}
{phang2}- Converted landscape option to page(landscape) option for esttab{p_end}
{phang2}- Improved handling of esttab_options by removing outer quotes{p_end}
{phang2}- Enhanced error checking for stored estimates{p_end}
{phang2}- Added reghdfe example to documentation{p_end}

